GYM-Trainer is an **AI-powered desktop fitness training application** built using **Python**, **OpenCV**, and **pose estimation**. It helps users perform workouts correctly by tracking body posture in real time through a webcam and counting repetitions automatically â€” **no gym equipment required**.

This project is ideal for:

* Beginners learning correct exercise posture
* Home workout enthusiasts
* Students exploring **Computer Vision + Fitness AI**

