---

## ğŸ¯ How It Works

1. User selects **body part** (Legs / Arms / etc.)
2. Chooses an **exercise** from the menu
3. Webcam starts capturing video
4. AI tracks body joints and angles
5. Correct reps are counted automatically

---

## â• Adding a New Exercise

1. Open `exercises/` folder
2. Add a new exercise class (example: `PushUp`)
3. Implement angle logic & rep counter
4. Register the exercise in `EXERCISE_MAP`
5. It will appear automatically in the GUI

